author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | The Jonathan Ross Show
text: Wossy continues his new series tonight as he welcomes another batch of celebrity guests to his famous green room. Tonight they include Martin Clunes and Strictly Come Dancing judge Darcey Bussell, while music will be provided by John Newman, who will no doubt be performing his crackin' new single 'I'm Not Your Man'.
